item.title: Microservices with .NET Core and Docker Episode 04 - Bandwidth Tester with Serilog and Seq
item.description:
A small project using Serilog and Seq. A worker service is doing a bandwidth test every few minutes. Serilog is logging the results to Seq where the average download and upload speed is displayed in a dashboard.
The nuget package used in the project: https://www.nuget.org/packages/SpeedTest/
